efire but it was literally 5 minutes before the servers went down for this weeks patch...  After Naggy died, our Ragefire popped roughly 28 hours later.  15 minutes later we had 40 people in the zone and he dropped like a brick (and he dropped a Cloak of Flames!  Woo Hoo!).<P>Both times the camp was respected.  We were not challanged and we never had to fight off another guild to maintain the camp or keep our Ragefire.<P>------------------<BR>Quistil Angelwatch<BR>Cleric of 44 Seasons in the service to the Great Mother Tunare<BR>Islington Angelwatch (Semi Retired)<BR>Paladin of 53 Seasons in the glorious service to Erollisi Marr<BR>Phoenix Crusaders</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
